OL,6,FFollowing our reporting, the Stormont
OL,7,FExecutive has withdrawn support for
OL,8,Fits literacy framework and told ITV
OL,9,FNews it will be launching a new
OL,10,Fstrategy based on the evidence of how
OL,11,Fchildren learn to read.
OL,13,FOne of the UK's leading reading
OL,14,Fscientists says ITV News's "vital
OL,15,Finvestigation" shows many children
OL,16,Facross the UK are getting "reading
OL,17,Finstruction that is not effective,"
OL,18,Fand has called on policymakers to
OL,19,Fcommit to providing "evidence-based
OL,20,Finstruction to all schools."
