OL,6,FThe controversial programme which
OL,7,Ffirst popularised cueing is called
OL,8,FReading Recovery. A long term study in
OL,9,F2022 found that the expensive one-on-
OL,10,Fone tutoring programme for young
OL,11,Fchildren had overall negative impacts
OL,12,Fon children.
OL,14,FDespite this, East Renfrewshire
OL,15,FCouncil and Education Scotland
OL,16,Frecently publicised its use of the
OL,17,Fprogramme on struggling readers.
