OL,6,FAt ten years old Thomas had an
OL,7,Femotional breakdown, telling his
OL,8,Fparents they would be "better off
OL,9,Fwithout him."
OL,11,FHis mum took him out of school to
OL,12,Fteach him to read herself using a
OL,13,Fsystematic synthetic phonics
OL,14,Fprogramme. Within three years Thomas
OL,15,Fwas fluent and is now thriving.
