OL,6,FMrs Millar has introduced a systematic
OL,7,Fsynthetic phonics approach in two
OL,8,Fschools which have led to remarkable
OL,9,Fturnarounds in reading outcomes,
OL,10,Fparticularly among disadvantaged
OL,11,Fstudents.
OL,13,FDespite this success, she was
OL,14,Finitially asked by her superiors why
OL,15,Fshe was going against government
OL,16,Fguidance. She insisted the results
OL,17,F"spoke for themselves."
