OL,6,F"We talk about equity, if we want to
OL,7,Flevel that playing field this is one
OL,8,Fof the simplest ways to do it. It
OL,9,Fdoesn't cost a lot of money, what it
OL,10,Fcosts is developing that skillset
OL,11,Fwithin the teachers."
OL,13,FMrs Millar says every child in
OL,14,FScotland should have the same
OL,15,Fadvantage through a systematic phonics
OL,16,Fapproach and regrets how she used to
OL,17,Fteach reading.
