OL,6,F"In my experience as a teacher - which
OL,7,Fis now 30 plus years - I have a guilt
OL,8,Fabout how I previously taught
OL,9,Fchildren. I think how on earth did
OL,10,Fthey learn?"
OL,12,FThe Scottish Education Secretary Jenny
OL,13,FGilruth wouldn't talk with us on
OL,14,Fcamera, and the department wouldn't
OL,15,Fanswer a direct question about whether
OL,16,Fchildren should be taught using cueing.
