OL,6,FIn a statement a spokesman said that
OL,7,Fit is up to schools to decide how to
OL,8,Fteach reading and that literacy levels
OL,9,Fin Scotland's schools are at a "record
OL,10,Fhigh."
OL,12,FThe spokesman added: "In 2024,
OL,13,FEducation Scotland published updated
OL,14,Fguidance and resources on early
OL,15,Freading which included guidance to
OL,16,Fschools on effective implementation of
OL,17,Fphonics as a key part of their overall
OL,18,Fapproach to teaching reading - however
OL,19,Fthis is just one approach to the
OL,20,Fteaching of reading."
