OL,6,FNorthern Ireland
OL,8,FSince 2011, the literacy framework in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland has also included a
OL,10,Freference to encouraging children to
OL,11,Fuse a "range of reading cues".
OL,13,FLast month, the education minister
OL,14,Fwithdrew his support for this strategy
OL,15,Fas it "implied cueing was an
OL,16,Facceptable form of teaching."
OL,18,F"Cueing is still very prevalent within
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland," says Nicky
OL,20,FHumphries, a specialist reading tutor.
