OL,6,F"Pupils are taught and encouraged that
OL,7,Fmeaning should be their first focus,"
OL,8,Fshe tells me, as well as being
OL,9,Fencouraged to "look at the picture" in
OL,10,Forder to read words.
OL,12,FIn an exclusive interview with ITV
OL,13,FNews, Education Minister Paul Givan
OL,14,Fsaid our investigation had
OL,15,Fdemonstrated there is a "clear
OL,16,Fchallenge as to what is going on in
OL,17,Fwithin our classrooms."
