OL,6,F"Our literacy framework in Northern
OL,7,FIreland has been based around phonics
OL,8,Fand systematic synthetic phonics is
OL,9,Fthe approach which is the most
OL,10,Ffundamental aspect to it.
OL,12,F"But there obviously was implied
OL,13,Freference to cueing as also being an
OL,14,Fapproach. So even though phonics is
OL,15,Fthe core, I felt that there were mixed
OL,16,Fmessages around that and that has now
OL,17,Fbeen withdrawn."
