OL,6,FMr Givan says he will be leading a
OL,7,F"new approach to literacy" which will
OL,8,Freflect the evidence of how children
OL,9,Flearn to read.
OL,11,F"In England, I look at the literacy
OL,12,Fspecialist hubs that are there that
OL,13,Fsupport schools, that has been
OL,14,Ftransformative. That is something that
OL,15,FI want to look at here in Northern
OL,16,FIreland.
