OL,4,Cteaching method after failings in Wales
OL,6,F"England has moved forward over the
OL,7,Fpast 10 years. We need to make sure
OL,8,Fthat Northern Ireland, from being in a
OL,9,Fgood place certainly on literacy, I
OL,10,Fthink we can do even more."
OL,12,FFollowing our investigation last year,
OL,13,Fthe Welsh government admitted it
OL,14,Fneeded to clarify its guidance to
OL,15,Fschools on the teaching of reading. We
OL,16,Fanalysed hundreds of school inspection
OL,17,Freports and found that inspectors not
OL,18,Fonly routinely praise the use of
OL,19,F"cueing" but on one occasion a school
OL,20,Fwas criticised for not using the long
OL,21,Fdebunked method.
