OL,6,FThe government later told ITV News
OL,7,Fchildren should not be using picture
OL,8,Fand context cues to decode words and
OL,9,Fit has opened a consultation which
OL,10,Fproposes several changes to its
OL,11,Fcurriculum framework. However, it is
OL,12,Fclear the message has not yet filtered
OL,13,Fthrough to its own local authorities,
OL,14,Flet alone classrooms.
