OL,4,Cteaching method after failings in Wales
OL,6,FCardiff Council is holding a training
OL,7,Fcourse for teachers in a programme
OL,8,Fcalled "Rainbow Reading" this week.
OL,9,FThe programme explicitly promotes
OL,10,Fcueing and downplays the importance of
OL,11,Fphonics. Neither Cardiff Council nor
OL,12,FRainbow Reading responded to a request
OL,13,Ffor comment.
OL,15,FBoth the Welsh curriculum and its
OL,16,FScottish equivalent give teachers
OL,17,Ffreedom in how they teach reading. But
OL,18,FDr Jeremy Law from the University of
OL,19,FGlasgow is concerned some teachers
OL,20,Faren't themselves taught about the
OL,21,Fscience of reading.
OL,26,@pD@HOUpD@XO]
