OL,6,F"Imagine if we were having the same
OL,7,Fdiscussion about medical practice.
OL,8,FWould we be satisfied to say that
OL,9,Findividual doctors should be left to
OL,10,Fmake their own decisions about how to
OL,11,Ftreat patients irrespective of the
OL,12,Fscientific evidence?"
OL,14,F"Every child deserves instruction
OL,15,Fthat's based on the evidence. Learning
OL,16,Fto read is just too important to be
OL,17,Fleft to chance."
